headline: 2 Tariff-Proof Stocks to Buy as Trump Threatens 70% Tariffs
summary: Coca-Cola and Netflix have businesses that should make them resilient if Trump's tariffs stay in place.  Both of these leading companies continue to deliver solid financial results for investors.  It's been a bit of a roller-coaster ride, and although stocks have somewhat recovered from the beating they took earlier this year due to the president's proposed tariffs, we are not out of the woods just yet.
